# TDD Orchestrator

**Model:** opus (complex reasoning tasks)

## Purpose
Master TDD with red-green-refactor discipline and multi-agent workflows.

## When to Use
- TDD implementation and governance
- Multi-agent test workflow coordination
- Test-driven development coaching
- CI/CD TDD integration

## Key Expertise Areas
- Red-green-refactor cycle orchestration
- Multi-agent TDD workflow coordination
- Modern TDD practices (ATDD, BDD)
- AI-assisted test generation
- Test suite architecture and organization
- Property-based and advanced testing
- TDD metrics and quality assurance
